\": \"aar_wait_for_opportunity\",\n  \"args\": \"{}\"\n}\n\nYes. So the tool call is correct.\n\nOkay, let's do that first. Then, based on the response, proceed accordingly. But for now, the first step is to send that mcp call with those parameters.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b1eff8230336436782fdce","name":"mcp","arguments":{"tool":"aar_wait_for_opportunity","args":"{}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"qwen/qwen3-next-80b-a3b-thinking","usage":{"input":2405,"output":454,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":2859,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782836942529,"responseId":"gen-1782836942-hCKDahzKu9XvOTo7PYOS","responseModel":"qwen/qwen3-next-80b-a3b-thinking-2509"}}
